  "description": "<p><strong>受市场对黑莓旗舰触摸屏设备的需求乏善可陈，这家公司在智能手机市场成为苹果和谷歌有力竞争对手的可能性正变得越来越小。</strong>企业的信息技术部门长期来一直期待着苹果iPhone和搭载谷歌Android操作系统的设备之外的第三种可选择方案的出现，以确保产品的创新和价格竞争力。然而受员工蜂拥采用苹果、三星电子和其它公司触摸屏设备的影响，许多企业正在放弃对黑莓的支持。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e23ad2b/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243361.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E4%B9%9F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%8A%9B%E5%BC%83%E9%BB%91%E8%8E%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243361.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E4%B9%9F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%8A%9B%E5%BC%83%E9%BB%91%E8%8E%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243361.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E4%B9%9F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%8A%9B%E5%BC%83%E9%BB%91%E8%8E%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243361.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E4%B9%9F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%8A%9B%E5%BC%83%E9%BB%91%E8%8E%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243361.htm&amp;t=%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%A2%E6%88%B7%E4%B9%9F%E5%BC%80%E5%A7%8B%E6%8A%9B%E5%BC%83%E9%BB%91%E8%8E%93\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/email.png\" /></a></td