  "description": "<p>用过双显示器的人都不愿意再重新使用单显示器，但一款显示器新品兼具了双显示器的优点，可能会让这些用户回心转意。<strong>冠捷科技</strong><a href=\"http://hothardware.com/Reviews/AOC-Q29630-29inch-UltraWide-IPS-LED-Monitor-Review/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">推出了</span></strong></a><strong>29 英寸Q2963PM LCD显示器，配备了一个超宽的IPS面板（如图），LED背光，分辨率2560x1080，宽高比21:9，178度垂直水平视角，内置画中画和画旁画 功能。测试显示，显示器可以同屏展示三页，能满足软件开发者需求，但没有三显示器方便。 </strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e23ad27/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243359.htm&amp;t=%E5%86%A0%E6%8D%B7%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA29%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B82560x1080+IPS+21%3A9%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%99%A8\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243359.htm&amp;t=%E5%86%A0%E6%8D%B7%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA29%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B82560x1080+IPS+21%3A9%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%99%A8\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243359.htm&amp;t=%E5%86%A0%E6%8D%B7%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA29%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B82560x1080+IPS+21%3A9%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%99%A8\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243359.htm&amp;t=%E5%86%A0%E6%8D%B7%E6%8E%A8%E5%87%BA29%E8%8B%B1%E5%AF%B82560x1080+IPS+21%3A9%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%99%A8\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%